Class ExerciseAerobic

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Exercise
      • model.ExerciseAerobic

  • public class ExerciseAerobic
extends Exercise
    This class contains all the information having to do with aerobic exercises. All information not here that is needed will be inside the Exercise class, which is extended by this class.
